0; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;'>📌&nbsp;</span>사용한 스킬 및 라이브러리</strong></h3><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><ul><li><p>React(Next.js), TailWind CSS, MongoDB, Firebase, Next-Auth, Toast UI Editor, AWS EC2 Linux</p></li></ul><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><p><img src='https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/simple-forum-f9e1c.appspot.com/o/post_images%2Ffpbw2ej9_202211722121253.png?alt=media&amp;amp;token=d76dd6ec-ad8d-4e56-b81f-ae12572cdfab' alt='image.png' contenteditable='false'><img class='ProseMirror-separator'><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><p>프론트 단은 Next.js, TailWind CSS로 구현됐으며, 로그인 인증은 Next.js/서버리스(Server less)에 유연한 Next-Auth 라이브러리와 bCrypt 암호화/reCaptcha를 사용해 회원 유저 검증을 진행합니다.</p><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><p>서버리스<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>환경에서<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> DB </span>접근은<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>클라이언트<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>요청으로<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> Next API</span>에서만<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>가능하도록<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>분리해<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>놓았으며<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'>, DB</span>는<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>자바스크립트와<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>호환성이<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>좋은<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> MongoDB</span>와<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>이미지<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>서버로<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> Firebase </span>스토리지를<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>사용하고<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>있습니다<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'>.</span></p><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><p>글 작성시 사용하는 위지윅(Wysiwyg) 에디터의 경우 Toast UI Editor를 적용했으며, 마지막 배포<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'>는 Vercel 대신 AWS EC2 </span>리눅스<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>서버에서<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> PM2 </span>프로세서<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>매니저를<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>통해<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'> </span>배포되었습니다<span class='s1' data-raw-html='span'>.</span></p><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><h3><strong><span data-raw-html='span' style='color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;'>📌</span> 개발하면서 작성한 포스팅</strong></h3><p><br class='ProseMirror-trailingBreak'></p><ul><li><p><strong><a href='https://juni-official.tistory.com/225' target='_blank'><span data-raw-html='span' style='color: #2f80ff'>[React] Next.js + Toast UI Editor 사용</span></a></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><a href='https://juni-official.tistory.com/226' target='_blank'><span data-raw-html='span' style='color: #2f80ff'>[React] 무한 스크롤(Infinite Scroll) 구현</span></a></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><a href='https://juni-official.tistory.com/227' target='_blank'><span data-raw-html='span' style='color: #2f80ff'>Firebase Storage 사용하지 않는 이미지 삭제하기</span></a>